Platform	Follower Goal	Growth Notes
HipHob	   100,000 followers	Viral-friendly, short content, low barrier to entry
LateGram	60,000 followers	Steady growth, highly visual, aesthetic-driven
Zirp	    30,000 followers	Harder to grow due to noise, but good for spikes
Dretit	     5,000 followers	Slowest growth, reputation > follower count
myPipe	    50,000 followers	Slow start, strong long-term retention

